    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You just received a love letter! But it's written with codes... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To read it you will need to solve the puzzles and get codes, which will serve to reveal the words of the letter. Each code is a word. Can you decipher what is written in the letter?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your <strong>mouse or arrow keys</strong> to draw the line. Fill the entire board and solve the puzzle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/5ee45cfa5269ad94775d95e1f7ad08b6.poster.avif?t=1760359944\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/5ee45cfa5269ad94775d95e1f7ad08b6.webm?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/5ee45cfa5269ad94775d95e1f7ad08b6.mp4?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Did something wrong? You can <strong>go back easily.</strong> Or just <strong>right click</strong> to delete the line wherever you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/5084ea51bffd2f497a3b49b75f3f7ebe.poster.avif?t=1760359944\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/5084ea51bffd2f497a3b49b75f3f7ebe.webm?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/5084ea51bffd2f497a3b49b75f3f7ebe.mp4?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After solving the puzzle you will get a <strong>code.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/d3454d655cb2a2a1dda2691cc323f1fc.poster.avif?t=1760359944\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/d3454d655cb2a2a1dda2691cc323f1fc.webm?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/d3454d655cb2a2a1dda2691cc323f1fc.mp4?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Find the code</strong> on the letter and <strong>discover</strong> the secret word.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/493ec3d7e028c89131024dc0663164c4.poster.avif?t=1760359944\" width=600 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/493ec3d7e028c89131024dc0663164c4.webm?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871500/extras/493ec3d7e028c89131024dc0663164c4.mp4?t=1760359944\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Features</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No tutorial. <strong>Straight to the game</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Minimalist design</strong>. No score, timer or pressure. Solve the puzzle in your time and enjoy the game experience.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >40 unique levels, with <strong>progressive difficulty</strong>.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get a code</strong> at the end of each level to reveal a piece of the letter.</p></li></ul>",
